    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You rush towards a target before unleashing a volley of attacks. Make two taijutsu attacks on a creature within range. On a hit you deal your unarmed damage + 1d6. If you hit with two or more of these attacks the target is knocked prone.</p><p><strong>At Higher Ranks:</strong> For each rank you cast this jutsu above D-Rank increase the cost of the jutsu by 3 and increase the damage by 1d6. If this jutsu is cast at B- Rank of higher increase the number of attacks by +1.</p>",
